Description:
You find a heavily guarded caravan of owls.

In one of the caravans, you can see how they transport several beavers in cages. You realize that one of them is about to open the cage and free himself.

If you want you could help him and make sure he escapes, although surely the owls will see you and chase you. On the other hand, you could alert the owls that there is a beaver about to escape.
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
